doctype html
html
  head
    title Select Profile
  body
    form action="/show" method="GET" 
      label for="name"
        | Select Profile
      select name="name" 
        - @profiles["profiles"].each do |key,value|
          option value="#{key}"
            = value["name"]
      button type="send"
        | Go
    div
      | When you're using Google Chrome, use option `--allow-file-access-from-files`
